<template>
    <b-container>
        <b-row align-h="center">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <b-form-input v-model="text" placeholder="Email"></b-form-input>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
        <b-row align-h="center">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <b-form-input v-model="text" placeholder="First name"></b-form-input>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
        <b-row align-h="center">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <b-form-input v-model="text" placeholder="Last name"></b-form-input>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
        <b-row align-h="center">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <b-form-input v-model="text" placeholder="Password"></b-form-input>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
        <b-row align-h="center">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <b-form-input v-model="text" placeholder="Confirm password"></b-form-input>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
        <b-row align-h="end">
            <b-col cols="4">
                <button @click="login">Login</button>
            </b-col>
        </b-row>
    </b-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            title: "Hello, World!",
            content: "1234567890",
            text: ''
        }
    },
    methods: {
        login() {
            fetch("http://localhost:8080")
            .then((request) => request.text())
            .then((text) => this.content = text)

            this.content = "sent"
        }
    }
}
</script>

<style>
b-col {
    padding: 4pt;
}
</style>
